name: Quinny
content:
Quinny was a Besalisk bartender who worked aboard the New Republic space station Brooksdion.
Quinny first appeared in Star Wars canon in Age of Resistance - Poe Dameron 1, a comic penned by Tom Taylor and illustrated by Ramon Rosanas that was published on August 28, 2019. Quinny was originally created for the Star Wars Legends Blood Ties: A Tale of Jango and Boba Fett 2, a 2010 comic written by Tom Taylor and illustrated by Chris Scalf.
